"So this is the Bay of Pearls. It looks like they have those mermen working "
"hard!"
msgstr "这就是珍珠湾。人鱼们看来正被逼做苦工！"

#: data/scenarios/Heir_To_The_Throne/Bay_of_Pearls.cfg:169
msgid ""
"Indeed it does. It also looks like they have many, many troops. I should go "
"around the bay and distract some of them. You and the rest rescue the mermen!"
msgstr "的确。敌军军势看来浩大。我去散发它们的注意力。你等去救人鱼们！"

#: data/scenarios/Heir_To_The_Throne/Bay_of_Pearls.cfg:173
msgid "Very well. Be careful!"
msgstr "好把。您可要小心点啊！"

# Tentative translation for Naga:
# Bay/Sea Of Pearls Dragon
