"东南 – 丹统\n"
"东北 – 谭关"

#: data/scenarios/Heir_To_The_Throne/Crossroads.cfg:272
msgid "Dan'Tonk, we are so close to Weldyn."
msgstr "丹统，我们已近魏玲。"

